# Copy to rlx.path (gitignored) to point scripts/ensure-rlx.sh at a non-default
# local RLX checkout. ensure-rlx.sh registers a cargo `paths` override (in
# ../.cargo/config.toml, outside the repo) so local builds resolve rlx from here;
# CI/published builds always use crates.io. Default: /Users/Shared/rlx
/Users/Shared/rlx
